com.rds_software.customers.menarini.projects.odp.model

Class OdpSearchCriteria

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rds_software.customers.menarini.projects.odp.model.OdpSearchCriteria

  • public class OdpSearchCriteria
extends Object
    Search criteria for filtering ODPs (Ordine di Pagamento). Used to specify search parameters when querying payment orders.

    This is a framework-independent POJO that serves as a data transfer object between the presentation layer (forms) and the service layer. All fields are nullable - a null value means "do not filter by this criterion".
